<db:section xml:id="sentenceEndingCharacters-prop">
<db:title>sentenceEndingCharacters : QString</db:title>
<db:para>This property specifies the sentence ending characters which will cause shift state change.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the property is initialized to sentence ending characters found in the ASCII range (i.e. &quot;.!?&quot;).</db:para>
